rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />cs都拎出黎講<br />\n<br />\n利申：想讀"},{"pid":"af4e114cdc9b0938dbb5132d27f504480fa546d1","tid":12130,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好同意樓主講既野，如果想效果更好就MAJOR CS再MINOR 一兩科engine/ba 野，出到黎更好撈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申EE 撚，又唔係話搵唔到工，但覺得識programming 前景會好好多，因為只要同hardware 有關既野就會有一定既standard 無創新可言，(一般)都唔需要好勁既人去做，識得programming 就可以做自動化野，利如機械人個D，好萄葡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真識讀一定讀CE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCivil Engineering<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> CE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜三大最低分既cu engine冇得讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n硬又得軟又得既真男人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3733b71effb9cef46dff361a9399a9d5a469cff1","tid":12130,"uid":14158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T10:58:48.000Z","msg":"IT狗 你的..........."},{"pid":"77ef1b6438e17098e61d2147c91cc844759266be","tid":12130,"uid":3112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"CS 老實講唔算係engineering , 係偏science多d<br />\n<br />\nmaterial science 同理<br />\n<br />\n樓主呢d 論點我以前係高登有開post 講過<br />\n<br />\n作為一個已轉field 既前香港工程撚，將香港既engineering 生態同外國（唔洗歐美，近近地強國同台灣已經夠做）比，實在就係得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n香港班所謂又chartered 又registered 又authorised 既engineer 係做咩duties ? checking , project management , 簽名（狽飛）。<br />\n<br />\n外國班engineer 又做咩duties ? design and calculations , innovations , project management<br />\n<br />\n係香港你問design 既detail 野 , calculations 野分分鐘technical grade 既staff ,甚至graduate engineer會仲清楚。<br />\n<br />\n真係好難想像到呢種organisation structure 會有幾progressive 同 innovative <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上香港engineering field 比construction dominate 左，非construction-related 既engineering 係香港可以有咩生存空間？<br />\n<br />\n非香港既 engineering student 有幾多個會揀electrical engineering (英式）而棄 electronic engineering ? 係美國，electrical engineering (美式）既energy and power specialisation 仲要出動哂scholarship 呀job offer 呀吸引人讀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n更加唔好提一堆mech 人以入building services field 為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人不如面對下現實，專心搞金融房地產好過啦，咩創科局呀科研呀生物醫學呀，係香港政府同商界利益主導下，根本唔會有咩作為。"},{"pid":"3f1f76a148846b5368875e82c7eeaff9b5c8d484","tid":12130,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>CS 老實講唔算係engineering , 係偏science多d<br />\n<br />\nmaterial science 同理<br />\n<br />\n樓主呢d 論點我以前係高登有開post 講過<br />\n<br />\n作為一個已轉field 既前香港工程撚，將香港既engineering 生態同外國（唔洗歐美，近近地強國同台灣已經夠做）比，實在就係得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n香港班所謂又chartered 又registered 又authorised 既engineer 係做咩duties ? checking , project management , 簽名（狽飛）。<br />\n<br />\n外國班engineer 又做咩duties ? design and calculations , innovations , project management<br />\n<br />\n係香港你問design 既detail 野 , calculations 野分分鐘technical grade 既staff ,甚至graduate engineer會仲清楚。<br />\n<br />\n真係好難想像到呢種organisation structure 會有幾progressive 同 innovative <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加上香港engineering field 比construction dominate 左，非construction-related 既engineering 係香港可以有咩生存空間？<br />\n<br />\n非香港既 engineering student 有幾多個